Class AugmentaP5

  • java.lang.Object
    • processing.core.PApplet
      • augmentaP5.AugmentaP5
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    processing.core.PConstants

    public class AugmentaP5
extends processing.core.PApplet
    Augmenta Connection: Connects to Augmenta app and provides your applet with Augmenta People objects as they arrive. This library is based on the TSPS library for processing. More details at http://www.tsps.cc/

    • Constructor Detail

      • AugmentaP5

        public AugmentaP5(processing.core.PApplet _parent)
        Starts up Augmenta with the default port (12000). Will also attempt to set up default Augmenta events, so will look for three methods implemented in your app: void personEntered( AugmentaPerson p); void personUpdated( AugmentaPerson p); void personWillLeave( AugmentaPerson p);
        Parameters:
        PApplet - _parent Your app (pass in as "this")

      • AugmentaP5

        public AugmentaP5(processing.core.PApplet _parent,
                  int port)
        Starts up Augmenta with a specific port. The port must match what is specified in the Augmenta GUI. Will also attempt to set up default Augmenta events, so will look for three methods implemented in your app: void personEntered( AugmentaPerson p); void personUpdated( AugmentaPerson p); void personWillLeave( AugmentaPerson p);
        Parameters:
        PApplet - _parent Your app (pass in as "this")
        int - Port set in Augmenta app
